                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The ledalusca freezes their surface into a translucent, faintly colored ice sculpture matching the mirror image of a Medium creature or object they have seen before. While in this form, instead of a wave, they have the following Strike:</p>\n<p><strong>Melee</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">a</span> ice shell [[/r 1d20+10]], <strong>Damage</strong> [[/r {1d6+4}]]{1d6+4 physical damage} plus [[/r {1d4}[cold]]]{1d4 cold damage}</p>\n<p>The physical damage is a type that matches the new shape of the ledalusca's frozen shell. The ledalusca can revert to their liquid form by taking this action again.</p>"
